<LP>
   JOHNSTON INDUSTRIES Inc. declared its first quarterly
dividend of 12.5 cents a share, payable Sept. 28 to stock of
record Aug. 24. The New York maker of industrial textiles,
which has about 4.7 million shares outstanding, had paid a
special dividend of 50 cents a share last September.
